## Basic Settings ##

set autoindent          " Automatically indent new lines based on the previous line
set constantshow        " Always show the current cursor position
set linenumbers         " Display line numbers in the margin
set mouse               " Enable mouse support
set softwrap            " Soft-wrap long lines at word boundaries
set tabsize 4           " Display tab characters as 4 spaces wide
set tabstospaces        " Convert literal tab characters into spaces

## Valid Key Bindings ##

bind ^Q exit main         " Bind Ctrl+Q to exit Nano
bind ^S writeout main     " Bind Ctrl+S to save (write out file)
bind ^K cut main           " Also bind Ctrl+K to cut text (duplicate binding if you prefer)

## Include additional nanorc files

include "~/.nano/*.nanorc"
